      <title>关税通过东南亚股票撕裂，越南市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/southeast-asian-currencies-stocks-highly-exposed-to-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）向东南亚的股票和货币降低了一些最大的关税税率。越南人共享。]]></description>
